<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="238" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,150,358]" pageId="7" pageNumber="238">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,338,258,284]" pageId="7" pageNumber="238">Comments:</emphasis>
This species is easily identifiable by the bluish metallic metasoma with white pubescence on the posterior margin of terga and sterna, as well as by the yellow hairs with black tips on mesoscutum, mesoscutellum and vertex. This species was correctly interpreted by 
<bibRefCitation author="Moure, J. S." box="[747,906,331,358]" pageId="7" pageNumber="238" pagination="114 - 123" refId="ref22477" refString="Moure, J. S. (1969) Notas sobre algumas especies de Centris da Guiana (Hym., Apoidea). Anais da Academia Brasileira de Ciencias, 41 (1), 114 - 123." type="journal article" year="1969">Moure (1969)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
